1143119 iif the company admits the full amount of the debt or claim, or, though not admitting it, is willing to provide for it, then, the full amount of the debt or claim;
1509980 iiif the company does not admit and is not willing to provide for the full amount of the debt or claim, or if the amount is contingent or not, ascertained, then, an amount fixed by the Court after the like inquiry and adjudication as if the company were being wound up by the Court.
